Title: Long Term Safety Observation of Crizotinib in Chinese NSCLC Population
Conditions: ALK or ROS1-positive NSCLC
Phase: PHASE4
Status: TERMINATED
Primary outcomes: Number of Participants With Grade 3 or 4 Adverse Events (AEs), Grade 5 AEs, AEs Lead to Treatment Discontinuation, Serious AEs (SAEs)- All Causality: Assessed by National Cancer Institute Common Terminology Criteria for Adverse Events (NCI CTCAE) v4.03; Number of Participants With Grade 3 or 4 AEs, Grade 5 AEs, AEs Leading to Treatment Discontinuation and SAEs- Treatment Related: Assessed by NCI CTCAE v4.03